{"TopicId":142966,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Console KSP Lifespan","CreatedByName":"KJ2022","CreatedById":109901,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T12:57:37Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"KJ2022","CreatedById":109901,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T12:57:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith KSP launching this month on PS4 and Xbox One, how many of you guys think the game will die very quickly without mod support?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"stibbons","CreatedById":57865,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T12:59:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that it\u0027s great that you\u0027re trying to build a community by preemptively trashing large portions of it. Great work, you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KJ2022","CreatedById":109901,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T13:00:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not trying to trash it, I enjoy the game both with and without mods, but a large portion of gameplay on youtube features mods, some console users could feel pushed out because of that?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HoloYolo","CreatedById":138353,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T13:02:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think it will last very long. The game is going to be extremely hard on console and people will have to relearn or just learn the game again. No mod support either would be a slap in the face too.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"stibbons","CreatedById":57865,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T13:04:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo many people who don\u0027t play on consoles having an opinion about consoles.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HoloYolo","CreatedById":138353,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T13:05:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222658305\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142966\u0022 data-ipsquote-c