12\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467464824\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022138353\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HoloYolo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, HoloYolo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a question. He\u0027s not trying to trash it, he\u0027s just seeing what other people would think.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich part of it was positive?\u00A0And, for bonus points, which part of it was not an hilariously leading question?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HoloYolo","CreatedById":138353,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T13:09:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222658313\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467464825\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257865\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022stibbons\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, stibbons said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nConsole critics don\u0027t make console games either. They play them. But I\u0027m sure you were going somewhere relevant here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, SQUAD hasn\u0027t even previewed them or showed us a closed alpha or beta. We\u0027re not going to know until Monday. It will probably be a whole other game. We don\u0027t know. But you don\u0027t have to be the way you are now about this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"stibbons","CreatedById":57865,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T13:11:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222658318\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467464946\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022138353\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HoloYolo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, HoloYolo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt will probably be a whole other game. We don\u0027t know. But you don\u0027t have to be the way you are now about this.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re right. We don\u0027t know. So it\u0027s unfair to have an opinion one way or the other. How does that tie in to \u0022the way I am now about this\u0022?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HoloYolo","CreatedById":138353,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T13:22:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222658321\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467465103\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257865\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022stibbons\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, stibbons said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re right. We don\u0027t know. So it\u0027s unfair to have an opinion one way or the other. How does that tie in to \u0022the way I am now about this\u0022?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou just seemed defensive, or maybe even mad. I\u0027m sorry if you aren\u0027t or are, but I guess you are right.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"stibbons","CreatedById":57865,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T13:31:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, right again. I bring reason in to a discussion about how porting KSP to consoles will destroy everything, and I\u0027m the one who\u0027s mad. You\u0027re on a roll.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MaxPeck","CreatedById":145248,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T13:57:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222658330\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467466303\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257865\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022stibbons\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n25 minutes ago, stibbons said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, right again. I bring reason in to a discussion about how porting KSP to consoles will destroy everything, and I\u0027m the one who\u0027s mad. You\u0027re on a roll.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDude, have a Snickers bar.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corona688","CreatedById":2511,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T14:00:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike minecraft on console vs minecraft on PC, it\u0027s going to be a somewhat different game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRemember, these will be primarily \u003Cstrong\u003Enew players\u003C/strong\u003E, ones who haven\u0027t spent the last 4 years wringing out every possibility of the game;\u00A0 they will also be \u003Cstrong\u003Econsole\u003C/strong\u003E players, used to the limitations console games face in general.\u00A0 I think they will also be somewhat younger on average.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo, they\u0027re not going to run around in circles and tear their hair out like distressed rabbits.\u00A0 Instead, like minecraft on console vs minecraft on PC vs minecraft on tablet, there will be relatively separate playerbases.\u00A0 That is what everyone is \u003Cstrong\u003Ereally\u003C/strong\u003E dreading, I think, an influx of newbies.\u00A0 Too bad.\u00A0 We were all newbies once.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSquad ought to start setting up wiki and forum spaces for that pretty much immediately though, if it\u0027s not there on launch there \u003Cstrong\u003Ewill\u003C/strong\u003E be confusion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-02T14:07:26Z\u0022 title=\u002207/02/2016 02:07  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 2, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Corona688\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T14:34:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222658307\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467464741\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022138353\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HoloYolo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, HoloYolo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMovie critics don\u0027t make movies do they?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut they do tend to watch a movie \u003Cem\u003Ebefore \u003C/em\u003Ewriting about it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-07-02T14:34:50Z\u0022 title=\u002207/02/2016 02:34  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 2, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Kerbart\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"stibbons","CreatedById":57865,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T15:22:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222658360\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467467862\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145248\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MaxPeck\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, MaxPeck said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDude, have a Snickers bar.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey, thanks for your contribution. I\u0027m not sure how it applies to this discussion though. Would you care to elaborate a little?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corona688","CreatedById":2511,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T15:46:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCongratulations, \u003Cstrong\u003Eyou\u003C/strong\u003E have let \u003Cstrong\u003Ehim\u003C/strong\u003E derail you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust lighten up and ignore it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Violent Jeb","CreatedById":130681,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T16:17:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n[redacted, done]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-08-16T14:36:02Z\u0022 title=\u002208/16/2016 02:36  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 16, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Violent Jeb\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nosirrbro","CreatedById":69814,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T17:05:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222658330\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467466303\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257865\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022stibbons\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, stibbons said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, right again. I bring reason in to a discussion about how porting KSP to consoles will destroy everything, and I\u0027m the one who\u0027s mad. You\u0027re on a roll.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone likes their consoles a\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Elittle\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0bit too much.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"the_Demongod","CreatedById":150124,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T17:16:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222658460\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142966\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221467476225\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022130681\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Violent Jeb\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n53 minutes ago, Violent Jeb said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0027t beat the controller for first person games (imo)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReally? What kind of first person games? Obviously FPS like Battlefield are far better on mouse simply from a precision standpoint, and I\u0027m having trouble coming up with other first person games that wouldn\u0027t suffer from that. 3rd person games\u00A0(like the Witcher, Dark Souls, etc) definitely work well with controllers, but first person with a controller\u00A0is extremely clumsy and\u00A0a player\u00A0with\u00A0mouse\u002Bkeyboard will beat a controller any day of the week. A game like KSP might be even worse though, since it literally relies on the mouse in the way that the rest of the operating system does (i.e. clicking on things on screen, not just moving it to look around), so I\u0027m interested in seeing how Squad prevents selecting things from becoming typing-with-a-controller-simulator-2016.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-07-02T17:17:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think the question is a legitimate one. I certainly wouldn\u0027t have stuck with KSP for so long without mods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat said:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- We don\u0027t know if the console versions will support mods or not. (I suspect not, but that hasn\u0027t been officially confirmed afaik.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- We don\u0027t know how good/bad KSP will be on consoles. Will it perform adequately? Will the control scheme be serviceable? Will it update at the same pace as the PC version?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThese questions are, IMO, the critical ones to KSP\u0027s success on consoles.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}